features: ★[ ECO-Friendly ] Made of 100% recyclable natural material to keep your mouth fresh while reducing the negative environmental impact.
★[ Biodegradable Handle ] The handle is made of pure natural degradable bamboo, sustainable and biodegradable, that can easily be recycled. Even the packaging is 100% recyclable.
★[ Medium Bristles ] BPA-free, charcoal-infused bristles will make you feel cleaner after brushing your teeth and gums, it can clean hard to reach areas.
★[ 10 Toothbrushes ] 5 individual boxes, each box containing 2 bamboo toothbrushes. Use colors and numbers to distinguish each toothbrush, suitable for family members.
★[ Guaranteed ] Money-back guarantee if you’re not completely satisfied within 120 days.
body.description: YOUR CHOICES ARE CRUCIAL--By opting for our bamboo toothbrush, you contribute to minimizing daily plastic usage, crucial for preserving our marine environments already burdened by excessive plastic waste. MATERIAL--Crafted from bamboo, a renewable resource, our toothbrushes ensure sustainable practices. Bamboo grows quickly, alleviating concerns about deforestation and loss of forests. MEDIUM BRISTLES--Medium bristles can assist in more effectively removing food residues from your oral cavity, and promote effective oral care with an eco-friendly touch. PACKAGING--Our toothbrush packaging is recyclable. We are committed to minimizing our ecological footprint from production to disposal. STORE--To extend the lifespan of your bamboo toothbrush, store it in a dry, well-ventilated environment when not in use. Avoid placing it in areas with excessive moisture, such as underneath bathroom sinks, ensuring both hygiene and durability.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love these, but confusing listing/packaging
reviews.reviewText: Let me start off by saying I love these. First time using wooden toothbrushes, and I have no complaints.However the listing title lists them as medium firm, but the description and box list them as soft. Fair warning, these are absolutely medium firm and not soft. Worked out for me since I don't like soft brushes, but not so much if you don't. So avoid this listing if you're looking for gentle bristles.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I personally love these, I always use kids toothbrush because it’s easier to work around my mouth. They last a long time and they are eco-friendly!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love these bamboo brushes
reviews.reviewText: Perfect price for the amount you received. I only use tooth brushes like these and they are super difficult to find in store for a good price. I no longer live near a TJ maxx or Marshall’s so I can’t just zoom to the store. Found these on Amazon and they will be repeat buys!

reviews.reviewText: These ones have rounded edges that make it more comfortable than other wooden toothbrushes I've gotten. 100% paper packaging! The white ones seem a bit softer bristled than the black, but the black ones are still soft.
